		<title>Mayo Clinic Minute: Rainbows Cancer Clinic helps the LGBTQ+ community navigate breast cancer</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-minute-rainbows-cancer-clinic-helps-the-lgbtq-community-navigate-breast-cancer/</link>
		
